  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of the study is to measure changes in physical functioning in chronic obstructive
      pulmonary disease (COPD) patients being treated with Spiolto® Respimat® after approximately 6
      weeks in routine clinical practice.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
